  "difficultyLevel": 6,
  "lyrics": "Yeah, I'm coming on through, you and me, see eternity like the flowers here, you and me, see eternity here like the flowers you waste, dancing all night, we're dancing all night in the flowers of our demise. Heartbreak, heartbreak, give me a little bit of your mistake, cause only heartbreak, heartbreak, give me a little bit of this we take, now I see you there with flowers in the night, I'm asking you to hold on tight, don't kill us, yeah, there's a way we can make it out alone, all I need is your flowers next to me, all I can need is your hand in mine, don't go, don't go with the flowers that's next to us, oh, you're only another disaster of the thought of us, don't leave me alone in the night, only thinking that we can only get it right, don't leave me alone in the night, as we try to get it right, all your flowers around me I see, it's the destiny of death here inside me, as I watch you walk away, I see me coming in clearer, is it hate, is it lust, is it something that we can't rise above, the only thing that we need are the flowers of the death of you and me, I see you there now looking for me in the death zone, I can't find my way to replenish the life that we made,",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 26.440000534057617,
      "text": "Yeah, I'm coming on through, you and me, see eternity like the flowers here, you and me,",
      "start": 12.039999961853027
    },
    {
      "end": 38.619998931884766,
      "text": "see eternity here like the flowers you waste, dancing all night, we're dancing all night in the flowers of our demise.",
      "start": 26.440000534057617
    },
    {
      "end": 53.86000061035156,
      "text": "Heartbreak, heartbreak, give me a little bit of your mistake,",
      "start": 47.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 62.400001525878906,
      "text": "cause only heartbreak, heartbreak, give me a little bit of this we take,",
      "start": 53.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 71.27999877929688,
      "text": "now I see you there with flowers in the night, I'm asking you to hold on tight,",
      "start": 63.97999954223633
    },
    {
      "end": 78.08000183105469,
      "text": "don't kill us, yeah, there's a way we can make it out alone,",
      "start": 71.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 93.62000274658203,
      "text": "all I need is your flowers next to me, all I can need is your hand in mine,",
      "start": 79.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 100.62000274658203,
      "text": "don't go, don't go with the flowers that's next to us,",
      "start": 93.62000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 109.31999969482422,
      "text": "oh, you're only another disaster of the thought of us,",
      "start": 101.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 116.55999755859375,
      "text": "don't leave me alone in the night, only thinking that we can only get it right,",
      "start": 109.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 124.62000274658203,
      "text": "don't leave me alone in the night, as we try to get it right,",
      "start": 116.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 132.72000122070312,
      "text": "all your flowers around me I see, it's the destiny of death here inside me,",
      "start": 124.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 140,
      "text": "as I watch you walk away, I see me coming in clearer,",
      "start": 133.3800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 147.75999450683594,
      "text": "is it hate, is it lust, is it something that we can't rise above,",
      "start": 140
    },
    {
      "end": 156.67999267578125,
      "text": "the only thing that we need are the flowers of the death of you and me,",
      "start": 147.8000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 163.6199951171875,
      "text": "I see you there now looking for me in the death zone,",
      "start": 157.4600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 172.17999267578125,
      "text": "I can't find my way to replenish the life that we made,",
      "start": 163.6199951171875
    }
